"""omlx-top — live TUI dashboard for oMLX server.

Requires macOS (Apple Silicon) and the ``rich`` Python package.

Controls:
  Up/Down or j/k  — select model
  Enter            — show model detail view
  Escape or q      — back to main view / quit
"""

